interpretation:
The Input Symbols card represents the language of technology and communication. It signifies the need for clear and concise communication in both personal and professional relationships. This card may also indicate the need to learn a new skill or language in order to better understand the world around you.

The Input Symbols card encourages us to embrace technology as a tool for communication and growth, but also reminds us to be mindful of the ways in which it can create barriers between us. This card may also indicate a need for organization and structure in your life, as the symbols on this card represent the building blocks of code and programming.

Overall, the Input Symbols card reminds us to be intentional in our communication and to use technology as a means of connection rather than a source of isolation. Embrace the language of technology, but don't forget the importance of human connection and understanding.
